snippet.title: defly.io: Building, fighting expanding territory
snippet.description:
Play at http://defly.io

Fly your helicopter and shoot at enemies
Build walls to protect yourself and conquer as much territory as possible
Fill areas to level up, upgrade your aircraft and buildings.
Use awesome superpowers to defeat your enemies!
